   "source": [
    "file has 20 for year, 9 for month — meaning September 2020. HYSPLIT stores 2-digit years, so you need 2000 + 20 = 2020. The parser handles this already."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "8281300c",
   "metadata": {
